'''我看見三隻船'''（'''I Saw Three Ships (Come Sailing In)'''）是一首傳統的[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[聖誕頌歌|聖誕頌歌]]，是“[[綠袖子|綠袖子]]”的變種，最早版本印刷於17世紀的[[德比郡|德比郡]]，1833年由[[威廉·桑蒂斯_(古文物研究者)|威廉·桑德斯]]再版。<ref>Cecil James Sharp (2008) [http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=3wk3HTOrvmYC&pg=PA9&dq=three+ships+-+variant+of+Greensleeves&hl=en&ei=k0MGTfGFOpGP4Aa51dy5Cg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CC0Q6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false The Morris Book: With a Description of Dances as Performed by the Morris Men] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=3wk3HTOrvmYC&pg=PA9&dq=three+ships+-+variant+of+Greensleeves&hl=en&ei=k0MGTfGFOpGP4Aa51dy5Cg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CC0Q6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20150104174032 }}</ref><ref name=HYM/> 歌曲描述的是航向[[伯利恒|伯利恒]]的船，不過實際上離此地最近的水域是20英里之外的[[死海|死海]]，而“三隻船”可能指的是12世紀用來將[[東方三博士|東方三博士]]遺骸運往[[科隆主教座堂|科隆主教座堂]]的三隻船。<ref name=HYM>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hymnsandcarolsofchristmas.com/Hymns_and_Carols/i_saw_three_ships.htm |title=Website describing the carol and giving secondary references |access-date=2013-10-05 |archive-date=2020-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225174537/http://www.hymnsandcarolsofchristmas.com/Hymns_and_Carols/i_saw_three_ships.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==變種==
* 我在新年看見三隻船駛來（I saw three ships come sailing by on New Year's Day）：19世紀版本，描寫三艘船上的三位姑娘在新年那天前去參加婚禮。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://www.gutenberg.org/cache/epub/25418/pg25418.txt|title=The Baby's Opera: A Book of Old Rhymes with New Dresses|last=Crane|first=Walter|authorlink=Walter Crane|pages=18–19|year=1877|publisher=[[Frederick_Warne_&_Co|Frederick Warne & Co]]|accessdate=7 October 2010|archive-date=2021-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108095306/https://www.gutenberg.org/cache/epub/25418/pg25418.txt}}</ref>

